data.description: Spacious home located in a prime location in Settler's Hammock. This home is located at the end of cul de sac with a large yard that backs up to state property, meaning you will always have a gorgeous view of the pond and wood line, no houses can  be built to ruin your view. It features 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, a formal dining room, home office, large kitchen and family room, the downstairs guest room has its own walk in closet and full bathroom, pub room, private sitting room in the master suite, and a spacious walk in closet.
data.whatILove: I love that this home is located in a beautiful community, at the end of the cul de sac, with a spacious backyard that will never have homes built behind. The bus stop is walking distance from the home, you can see the stop from the end of the driveway.
